prompts.prompt:
Create a well styled and beautiful component that lists the comments on a given jira issue. Add a fetch button that fetches the comments for the issue.
Use any relevant api or package to connect with jira. Also add a plus button that allows adding a new comment. Add proper error and null handling. 
Use the jira package https://www.npmjs.com/package/jira-client jira-client package version 8.2.2

Do not include comments in package.json

Add an example of the jira comments component to the index page. Add logic to pass in some example data which is shown as default on the component load if the fetch fails. 
Also add unit tests.
